Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:04.00,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2\fad(500,500)}翻译：绿豆  小怡       时间：恩底米昂之鹰       压制：Tanaous     后期：Salty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私設武裝組織天行者以根除戰爭為名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始武力介入世界範圍內產生的紛爭已經過了5年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在世界各地旅途奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注視著這因為天行者的武力介入而滿目瘡痍的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 這重生…是否能說是正確的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世間的扭曲 如今還慄然再目不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使們的軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.70,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}公元2301年 庫魯吉斯共和國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭是獻給神的聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24世紀初 世界從化石燃料時代轉變為太陽光發電時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:27.08,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}蔑視神聖 爭奪神之土地的無神論者們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.72,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我們將降下制裁的鐵錘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那場改革的戰爭中 幼小的我被捲入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這生與死的交錯之處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那台機體相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和命運的機體 Gundam相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2307年 我們私設武裝組織天行者開始了行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,240082 Exia 目標地點確認
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子散佈 在到達目標地點後終止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標對像確認
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照預定 開始第一階段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 竟然還有一台新機體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些光點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在2個世紀前死掉的天才宇宙物理學家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·肖漢博格所提言的世界的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙… 還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在模擬戰中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩千次…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敗的戰績啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 第一階段完成 開始第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為之而生的4台機體 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 目標瞄準狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 轟炸目標
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然變形了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 捕獲目標 日掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 光束劍!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.88,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ビームサーベル（Beem Saber）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要根絕戰爭之類的覺悟 讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的頭 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你得手麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續的對各個紛爭區域的武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,促成了我和某個男人命運的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及和某個人命運的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作被看透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈 機體不錯但駕駛員看來還嫩點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? Gundam先生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個勁只會打擾我做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和過去我所屬的游擊隊KPSA的頭目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里·阿魯·沙歇斯的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就收下了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞併了我的故國庫魯吉斯共和國的阿扎帝斯坦王國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其年輕的王女相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩莊際遇 逐漸交集到阿扎帝斯坦王國的內亂中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向忘記神的教導的人們給與神罰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅趕走那些進入契約之地的異教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生戰爭就會有人死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果紛爭繼續的話 總有一天我會去阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所做的事情 把這個國家引向了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡 我品嚐到了無盡的絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 當不了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 有機影正在接近這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UNION的偵查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那台白色的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 知道政變的主謀是沙歇斯後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就決定了再次戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要 為了成為Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到 那時候的小屁孩居然坐上了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的戰鬥還沒有結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯吉斯都毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的神在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒義務回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了 這機體還是讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這小子擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切按計劃進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可未必
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下 天行者組織發來了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者組織發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪被保護 正向王宮行進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而後 我慢慢的首次發現作為Gundam戰鬥的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放正保護的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放正保護的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是否還會前來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你所相信的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:22.86,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}UNION 大總統府
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.70,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}人革連 國家主席室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.91,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}AEU中央議會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了從世上根除戰爭而創立的武裝組織
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·肖漢博格的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是即由天行者的武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得世界能夠統一成一體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以擁有壓倒性武裝能力的Gundam為手段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將紛爭逐一擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一擊 結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子 開始裝填
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這數量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為了對抗我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是伊奧利亞計劃的一部分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了世界的統一而存在的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待我們的只有毀滅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的新的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所不知的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崔尼蒂小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也自稱是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們所進行的武力介入和我們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對各個軍事基地的無差別攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向一般市民攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸… 媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸! 媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易買下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又這麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒辦法戴上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Gundam的所為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 驅除目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不配做Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 萬死難辭其咎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就是三對三了 要公平競賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們相比 你有應該先解決的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該是 尼爾·狄蘭迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾·狄蘭迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那場戰鬥中 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我過去所屬的游擊隊KPSA發起的自殺性恐怖襲擊 而失去親人的洛克昂的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 此刻我幾乎無法抑制幹掉你的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了給我的家人報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的怨念得以平息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用Exia做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根絕戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我幹掉你就不能如願了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能代替我實現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我校正這畸形的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我還活著 我就會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非作為索蘭·依伯拉罕而是作為天行者的Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛著Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太傻瓜了 我都射不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個了不得的Gundam傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最好的稱讚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莢艙 打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我們的戰鬥迎來了最終的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載了GN drive的聯合國軍的猛攻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼只是擦到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有壓倒性優勢的Gundam的性能 如今也喪失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們的滅亡也是計劃裡的一步麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 和奪走Throne Zwei的亞里·阿魯·沙歇斯的再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的男人不配駕駛Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不需要你來許可!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這可就玩完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 那動作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放了 TRANS-AM系統
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 拉塞所說的話在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我認為天行者組織 我們的存在不是有意義的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那場戰鬥中 洛克昂和家族的仇人對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這製造戰爭的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使Dynames被破壞了 那個男人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽爐 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的 躲哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活體反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準射擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們滿意了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了消除紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是除了戰鬥一無所知的破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打倒眼前的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要糾正這扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即由武力的根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這才是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam所應有的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我 我們是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這4年裡 我一直在世界各地旅途奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注目著我們天行者 Gundam所引發的世界變革
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想 這重生…是否能說是正確的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世間的扭曲 如今還慄然再目不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還存在著扭曲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和新的機體 00 Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士Gundam 00 第二季
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度降臨的天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開新的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公元2312年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了地球聯邦政府的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創建了獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了以地球統一為名的鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了糾正這個扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者再次站了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新番組 機動戰士Gundam 00
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10月5日 週日下午5點 武力介入開始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那重生毀滅


